Title: Mycomayhem
Description:
Freydrin was the leader of my order. I was sent here to assist them. I was too late.

There is a darkness that haunts these woods, $rs.

These woods were Freydrin's home. It was her charge to tend to them, so given by the Keeper herself. And now she is gone and her woods run amok.

Bring me the spores of these mayhemic menaces. Perhaps there is a way to cleanse this land yet.
ObjectivesText: Collect 30 Boskroot Spores from fungarians in Boskroot Basin.
RewardText:
Thank you, $n. I will take a close look at them. The fungarians of these woods pose a greater danger than any of us anticipated.

We must be prevent their spread.
